# Biome Code Style

Biome is the only formatter and linter used in this repository.

## Formatting

- Indent with 4 spaces.
- Use LF line endings.
- Keep lines within 120 characters when practical.
- Use single quotes.
- Always use semicolons.
- Keep ES5 trailing commas.
- Use arrow-function parentheses only when needed.

## Linting

- Let Biome organize imports.
- Avoid unused imports and unused variables.
- Do not introduce ESLint or Prettier configuration.

## Notes

- The root `biome.json` is the source of truth.
- Respect repository ignores such as `dist`, `node_modules`, and generated files like `src/routeTree.gen.ts`.
